<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="holotype">
<paragraph pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Holotype:</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Ecuador</emphasis>
: 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Ecuador:</emphasis>
Orellana, Tiputini Biodiversity Station, Rio Tiputini, Erwin Transect, 232m, &quot;0.63173°S, 76.14420°W,&quot; 23 October 1998 (T.L. Erwin, et al.)(NMNH: 117233, female).
